---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<Base title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
  <section class="bio">
    <img class="bio-photo" src="/headshot.jpeg" alt="Portrait of Juthika Saxena" />
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>Juthika Saxena</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        I'm a finance transformation consultant at
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/dasjuthika" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">PwC</a>,
        working with organizations to improve finance processes, reporting,
        controls, and technology-led ways of working. My work sits at the
        intersection of finance, operations, people, and systems &mdash; helping
        teams move from fragmented, manual processes to cleaner, more
        insight-driven ways of working.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <p>
    Beyond consulting, I'm interested in how AI can make finance and business
    workflows faster, clearer, and more useful. I'm also involved in
    entrepreneurial ventures including <strong>Empire Raas</strong> and
    <a href="https://everything3dindia.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><strong>Everything 3D</strong></a>,
    which keep me close to customers, brand-building, operations, and
    real-world execution.
  </p>

  <p>
    Outside work, I'm a mother and someone who takes fitness seriously. For me,
    motherhood and workouts are not separate from my professional life &mdash;
    they shape how I think about discipline, energy, ambition, and growth. I
    share bits of that side of life on
    <a href="https://instagram.com/juthika.saxena" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Instagram</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>What I do</h2>
  <p>
    My work and interests sit across finance transformation, AI, entrepreneurship,
    and personal discipline. These may look like separate areas, but for me they
    share one thread: building better systems &mdash; at work, in business, and
    in life.
  </p>

  <div class="cards">
    <article>
      <h3>Finance transformation</h3>
      <p>
        Process improvement, reporting, controls, operating models, stakeholder
        management, and technology-led change.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h3>AI experiments</h3>
      <p>
        Practical use cases for AI in finance and consulting &mdash; documentation,
        analysis, reporting, synthesis, and productivity.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h3>Entrepreneurial ventures</h3>
      <p>
        Through Empire Raas and
        <a href="https://everything3dindia.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Everything 3D</a>,
        I stay close to the realities of building a business: customers,
        branding, operations, and execution.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h3>Motherhood &amp; fitness</h3>
      <p>
        Motherhood keeps me grounded. Fitness keeps me disciplined. Both shape
        how I think about time, energy, consistency, and growth.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <h2>Find me online</h2>
  <p>I occasionally share updates, reflections, and work across these spaces.</p>

  <div class="icon-links">
    <a
      class="icon-link"
      href="https://linkedin.com/in/dasjuthika"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noreferrer"
      aria-label="LinkedIn"
